headline: Q4 Industrial Packaging Earnings Review: First Prize Goes to Crown Holdings (NYSE:CCK)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at industrial packaging stocks, starting with Crown Holdings (NYSE:CCK).
